sponseOfProdutoCatalogoItemResponse:\r\n      type: object\r\n      properties:\r\n        pages:\r\n          pattern: \"^-?(?:0|[1-9]\\\\d*)$\"\r\n          type:\r\n          - integer\r\n          - string\r\n          format: int32\r\n        size:\r\n          pattern: \"^-?(?:0|[1-9]\\\\d*)$\"\r\n          type:\r\n          - integer\r\n          - string\r\n          format: int32\r\n        totalItems:\r\n          pattern: \"^-?(?:0|[1-9]\\\\d*)$\"\r\n          type:\r\n          - integer\r\n          - string\r\n          format: int64\r\n        data:\r\n          type: array\r\n          items:\r\n            \"$ref\": \"#/components/schemas/ProdutoCatalogoItemResponse\"\r\n    PedidoCanceladoResponse:\r\n      type: object\r\n      properties:\r\n        pedidoId:\r\n          pattern: \"^-?(?:0|[1-9]\\\\d*)$\"\r\ndocs/frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:38:│   │   ├── contracts/\r\ndocs/frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:53:- `features` organizam página, componentes, hooks, schemas, queries e mutations do próprio domínio.\r\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
